{"tid":1856083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"訛稱出售口罩 騙款逾16萬元被捕","createTime":"2020-02-01T12:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T17:03:06.000Z","uid":3195,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0cde94f06ca9b6ce9e21b86900499c0b6dd806","tid":1856083,"uid":3195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方拘捕一男一女，兩人涉嫌在網上訛稱有醫療口罩出售，騙取款項合共約16萬5千元。<br />\n<br />\n警方在行動中檢獲電腦及手提電話等證物，警方近日接獲多名受害人報案，指透過網上社交平台購買口罩，轉賬後未能收取貨物，賣家亦失去聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，分別在大埔及天水圍拘捕一名16歲男子及一名24歲女子。他們分別涉嫌串謀詐騙，及以欺騙手段取得財產，涉及款項合共16萬5千元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48433a85180e1cf1acf4d4474d13a31d5417827","tid":1856083,"uid":46042,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"求撚期都呃10幾萬<br />\n大把人成恭"},{"pid":"024e7ded90bdf6c2788796751a61522d1bf37f9f","tid":1856083,"uid":46042,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"之前嗰啲扮黃<br />\n話籌款 最後唔見咗 嗰啲個個呃拎10幾萬走"},{"pid":"7e8dc76e189284ee263f0205b443c4b0b39bc611","tid":1856083,"uid":3195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:18:54.000Z","msg":"補link: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=378908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378908&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=6f353506\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378908&h=a2b1d641\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=378908</a>"},{"pid":"694344d8d74f8ba65ea4aa74b065c75bccabcc26","tid":1856083,"uid":192528,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"024e7ded90bdf6c2788796751a61522d1bf37f9f","tid":1856083,"uid":46042,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"之前嗰啲扮黃<br />\n話籌款 最後唔見咗 嗰啲個個呃拎10幾萬走